title: Did the Obamacare Website Cost More Than What It Will Cost to Build Trump’s Border Wall?
subtitle: A spurious quote attributed to actor/comedian Tim Allen was shared by one of President Donald Trump's sons.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The Obamacare website, HealthCare.gov, cost more than what U.S. President Donald Trump's U.S.-Mexico border wall will cost.
